NOTE ON SCOPE
The MIT license above covers ONLY the source code in this repository
(HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and the Python scraper script).

It does NOT cover the video content, captions, thumbnails, or any other
material referenced in the JSON files under data/. That content remains the
property of the original Instagram creators (currently @demicstory and
@appyoucan). Embeds in this site link directly to Instagram's servers; this
project neither claims ownership of nor relicenses that content.

See README.md for credits and takedown instructions.
